data.description: UPDATE: Interior of the home has been newly painted, animals are gone, fresh bark has been added!  Motivated Seller! Let us help you fall in love with this home! Lexington location w/easy access to freeway and the beautiful new desirable Lexington school! Large entry, 4 bedrooms + a bonus office, full & 3/4 bath, Hardwoods, laminate & tile floors. Play area, a patio to relax, and a Shop w/lots of room for parking, storage, workbench; & RV  or boat parking. There really is something for everyone! Fenced, garden space & much more! Make your appt. to see….call your favorite REALTOR…if you don’t have one I’d love to chat with you about this home & our current market.  So many exciting & important changes for 2024 now in effect! See you soon!
